    "This underscores the effectiveness of Atleus which leverages the advantages of ReRAM-based PIM in reducing system energy for more than 90% of the computations, while preventing frequent writes on crossbars during fine-tuning.",
    "D. NoC OptimizationNext, we evaluate the performance of the NoC incorporated in Atleus.",
    "We examine three distinct NoC designs in terms of EDP, area, and cost for this evaluation:1) 3D-mesh: A 3D mesh enabled by TSV links.",
    "It serves as a reference point for comparison.",
    "2) 3D-mesh with skip: An extension of the 3D-mesh design where we introduce additional TSV-skip links connecting the top and bottom tier."
